-- LEARN GREEK — Part 4: Vocabulary Lessons (30)
-- =============================================
-- Run AFTER 03-greek-alphabet-data.sql
-- Lesson IDs 25–54 are reserved for vocabulary
-- 6 groups of 5 words each
